ic interaction in\nbi-layer manganite, we propose that the tri-layer\nLa$_{2.1}$Sr$_{1.9}$Mn$_{3}$O$_{10}$ should be able to host the skyrmion below\nT$ _{C} $ due to its strong anisotropy and layered structure.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 26 Nov 2020 18:43:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-11-30"}
