may appear correlated if they are controlled by any physical processes\non larger scales; this may lead to a high probability of chance alignment\nbetween older SN progenitors and younger stellar populations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 27 Nov 2020 11:08:42 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 7 Apr 2021 16:12:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-04-21"}
